# Pizza Sales Analysis (SQL Project)

## Overview
This project analyzes pizza sales data using SQL to extract business insights and understand sales performance.

## Tools Used
- SQL

## Key Analysis
- Total orders and revenue
- Top-selling pizzas
- Peak order hours
- Category-wise sales

## Key Insights
- Peak order time: 12–1 PM
- Identified best-selling pizza categories
- Analyzed revenue contribution by pizza type

## SQL Concepts Used
- Joins
- Aggregations (SUM, COUNT)
- Subqueries
- Window Functions

## Conclusion
This project helps understand customer behavior and sales trends to support data-driven decisions.
